<br>
Naladini said:<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>However, lets remember that the T Rod Nerf occurred at level 56. There was zero compensation for the nerf at that level.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--> To be fair, they did upgrade Transon's Phantasmal Protection to compensate for the mana loss. It was changed from 3 mana per tick to 5 I believe. Whether or not this is &quot;fair&quot; compensation is arguable I suppose.<br>
<br>
<br>
